{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We meet up with some very good friends of ours, Robert Weil and, and Fanny, a friend of mine from school, and two little children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, how come you are here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, yes, I saved 300 children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was member of the OSE.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] And he was at the Swiss border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was caught with his wife, who was 24, 23, and two little children-- four years and 18 months, something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were on their way to Switzerland because they went with the-- with the whole of the town to Cognac, to the other side.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were caught there, too, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were now with us in the same transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were hundreds and hundreds of people there, thousands of them there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the conditions were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we didn't know what was going to happen to us yet, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when-- we stayed-- a few days we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We stayed there in Drancy three, three nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We leave on the 30th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we must have stayed from May till the-- from the 18th-- from the-- five days about, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We stayed about five days in Drancy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they took us to the-- a whole-- 2,000 people they took to the station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was one case where the lorries that were standing there, the person that was there-- there was a woman there with a girl of about 10 or 12.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she pretended to be mad because she didn't want to go on a-- on, on, on the-- on the-- truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I can see only by hindsight, but she knew what was happening better than we did.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
